originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    t.production_year,
    c.kind AS company_type,
    k.keyword AS movie_keyword,
    pi.info AS person_info
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
LEFT JOIN 
    person_info pi ON a.person_id = pi.person_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
    AND k.keyword ILIKE '%thriller%'
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, a.name ASC
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "title"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "s1"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "person_info"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id"
LEFT JOIN "person_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "person_info"."person_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000 AND "s1"."keyword" ILIKE '%thriller%'
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "person_id", "info_type_id", "info", "note"
FROM "person_info"

SELECT COALESCE("aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "title"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "s1"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000 AND "keyword"."keyword" ILIKE '%thriller%'
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"
LIMIT 100
